{"tid":1318503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 依場仗唔易，有勇有謀仲好需要EQ","createTime":"2019-07-15T03:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T07:10:25.000Z","uid":61520,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ddd3969e791c75abef24636bc2fae0319729996","tid":1318503,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:00:33.000Z","msg":"今次場仗唔易打， 除左要有勇有謀 仲好需要高EQ<br />\n來緊會愈來愈多依啲三毛開咁樣既post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TeBPH6p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTeBPH6p.png&h=dda80ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家都會好嬲， 想回post 屌柒佢，但唔該停一停<br />\n諗一諗，唔好助長依啲post 置頂。。。。。。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論入面啲人點回post 都好 大家留下負評一笑置之就ok</span><br />\n<br />\n都唔好block 佢， 因為會有好多cd rom 睇， 你block 左就無得留負評 唔好同依啲三毛post 嘈， 唔好俾依啲三毛post 置頂<br />\n記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要係依個星期要將 713, 714 既事盡量廣傳，希望連登既熱門都係為721 集氣既post</span></span><br />\n<br />\n覺得同意既 推一推個post 俾多啲人了解<br />\n每個人出一分力，香港人仲可以救到香港，唔好睇少自己既一分力量 大家一齊加油<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5115a71c8acc0817bca153631ed36a797c8239e5","tid":1318503,"uid":241131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:01:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5e9c9d1da3ae16ba4d2a404d6d0b8735add2267e","tid":1318503,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:22:29.000Z","msg":"自推幾下"},{"pid":"bf674f3ed89ed04e188579a67134c92f556b35af","tid":1318503,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"[有冇搞撚錯] 你哋係咪打算揼低陳伯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.k